casebody.data:
TOWER LIEN, LLC, Plaintiff,
v.
Carlos CEPEDA, Defendant-Movant,
and
Wells Fargo Bank, N.A., Ramin Ghobadi, M.D. and State of New Jersey, Defendants. M-1086/1087 September Term 2017
079753 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-1087) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-1086) is denied.
